Optimizing the code:

1. code reusable
2. easy to maintain the codes
3. make it more object oriented programming

Follow below hierarchy:

1. main
2. Test
3. Action
4. CssSelectors



My projects loooks like this:

1. create "main" folder in "java" folder : tworzymy folder główny, w którym będziemy zapisywali nasze testy
2. create "mainTests" class in "main" folder: tutaj będą nasze testy
3. create another folder "Test" in "java" folder
4. create "testScenarios" in "tests" folder
5. create "Action" folder in "tests" folder
6. create "action" class in "Action" folder
7. create "CssSelectors" folder in "Action" folder
8. create "selectors" class in "CssSelectors" folder